column5: Set up camp for a 3 day long week-end fishing trip.   shore fishing is one of my all time fav.   drink/eat/fish/fire/nap/music/drink/eat/ FISH ON!
Winds from the north... well Kev... I think that wind sucks.  But your laker pic here... a doozie dood!  Cool shore shot!
Sweeeet sweet touladi.  Tis the season for shoreline bruisers
Great looking "La Grise" Dude Was that the only one???
i love soaking for lakers.  nothing like sitting on shore, drinking, grilling meat, and hitting roaming lakers on a dead smelt.
